564
00:28:23,827 --> 00:28:25,995
e desenvolvendo  Falsas Promessas  com Will.

565
00:28:26,955 --> 00:28:29,791
Tipo o centro de tratamento Promises 
de Malibu,

566
00:28:29,874 --> 00:28:31,376
mas ficcionalizado.

567
00:28:31,710 --> 00:28:32,544
